OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Pam Harding
OL,5,FPam Harding, Age: 102, Women's Royal
OL,6,FNaval Service
OL,8,FInterviewed 8 February 2024
OL,10,FBecoming a chief petty officer after
OL,11,Fpassing her morse code course, Betty
OL,12,FHarding was stationed at Abbots Cliff
OL,13,Fin Kent.
OL,15,FA fluent German speaker, she joined a
OL,16,Fteam listening into chatter from enemy
OL,17,Fships in the English Channel.
OL,19,FAbbots Cliff was at Capel le Ferne
OL,20,Fbetween Folkestone and Dover and had
OL,21,Fbeen operational since 1940.
