OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Pam Harding
OL,5,FInformation also helped the Allies
OL,6,Funderstand the movement of enemy
OL,7,Fshipping ahead of the invasion.
OL,9,FMrs Harding added: "By the time we
OL,10,Fwent on watch on 5 June, we had a very
OL,11,Fclear idea that something was
OL,12,Fhappening and we had unusually some
OL,13,Fnaval officers there and eventually
OL,14,Fthey did tell us that it was happening.
OL,16,F"So we thought we were doing something
OL,17,Fimportant, particularly once the
OL,18,Finvasion had started. We really felt
OL,19,Fpart of it."
