OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Pam Harding
OL,5,FMrs Harding also kept a diary and
OL,6,Frecalled seeing many ships in the
OL,7,FEnglish Channel on D-Day, including
OL,8,Fone in a convoy which had caught fire.
OL,10,FShe was later posted to France until
OL,11,Fthe end of the war in Europe and then
OL,12,FGermany before being demobbed in 1946.
